Write the program to find power of a number using recursion.

Input & Output Format:

Input consists of two integers.

First input consists of a value.

Second input consists of a power value.

Output consists of one integer.

Sample Input

5

2

Sample Output


5 to the power 2 is 25

//coding

#include<iostream>
#include<math.h>
using namespace std;
int val(int a,int b)
{
    int c;
    c=pow(a,b);
    return c;
}
int main()
{
    int a,b;
    cin>>a>>b;
    cout<<a<<" to the power "<<b<<" is "<<val(a,b);
}
